{"title":"白洋淀（二首）","authors":["萧振荣"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":7,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"白洋淀（二首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萧振荣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"荷花淀拾忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉在湖底的战争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早已沤作历史，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肥沃着荷花淀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那别样红的记忆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来时似箭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"归去依依，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只为小小游艇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"载不动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雁翎队许多传奇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远望采蒲台"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白洋淀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一首清新的田园诗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采蒲台"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是她青翠欲滴的诗眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早从这水灵灵的名字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"采得一束绿色的灵感，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此刻，你淡墨般的水村，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朦胧地挂在艄公篙尖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就这样，就这样远远读你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美，原本就不宜近看；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更何况，我愿意想象"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你眼底那抹揩不掉的硝烟……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}